            </div>
            <div class="blog-row2">
                <div class="blog-post">
                    <div class="blog-head">
                        <img src="homepage/7/Rectangle 19.jpg" alt="Blog-Image">
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog-body">
                        <h3>10 Reasons you should buy an escooter in 2023 <span>14/07/2022</span></h3>
                    </div>
